{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847757242,"sessionID":"ses_28739d782ffesMLvrTsRXAlpsf","part":{"id":"prt_d78c64eea001dqPeafuZDSv9uS","messageID":"msg_d78c64252001zYCgDHqNC1DMkv","sessionID":"ses_28739d782ffesMLvrTsRXAlpsf","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_4b49a923f523422cbe68f553","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/agentd\n4: **Language:** Go\n5: **Size:** S\n6: \n7: ## 目的\n8: \n9: 为 AgentCube 实现一个独立的 `agentd` 组件，基于 controller-runtime 构建 Sandbox 资源的空闲清理控制器。当 Sandbox 的 `last-activity-time` 注解标识的最后活动时间超过 15 分钟（`SessionExpirationTimeout`）时，控制器自动删除该 Sandbox，释放集群资源。\n10: \n11: 当前沙箱的空闲清理逻辑由 WorkloadManager 的 `LifecycleManager` 通过轮询 Store（Redis）实现，存在以下局限：\n12: - 依赖外部 Store，Store 不可用时清理失效\n13: - 轮询间隔（默认 5 分钟）导致清理延迟\n14: - 无法利用 Kubernetes 原生 watch 机制实时响应 Sandbox 状态变化\n15: \n16: `agentd` 作为独立的 in-cluster 控制器，直接 watch Sandbox CR 的创建/更新事件，通过 requeue 机制在精确的过期时间点触发删除，提供更可靠、低延迟的空闲清理能力。\n17: \n18: ## 范围\n19: \n20: ### 包含\n21: \n22: 1. **Reconciler 实现**\n23:    - `Reconciler` 结构体：嵌入 `client.Client`，持有 `*runtime.Scheme`\n24:    - `Reconcile(ctx, req)` 方法：实现 Sandbox 空闲检测与删除的核心逻辑\n25:    - 从 Sandbox 注解 `last-activity-time`（`workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey`）读取最后活动时间\n26:    - 解析 RFC3339 格式时间戳，计算 `expirationTime = lastActivity + SessionExpirationTimeout`\n27:    - 过期时调用 `Delete`，未过期时 `RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)`\n28: \n29: 2. **SetupWithManager**\n30:    - 注册 Sandbox 资源的 controller-runtime watch\n31:    - 使用 `ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).Complete(r)` 模式\n32: \n33: 3. **Binary `cmd/agentd/main.go`**\n34:    - Scheme 注册：core Kubernetes 类型 + `sandboxv1alpha1`（`sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`）\n35:    - 构造 controller-runtime Manager：禁用 metrics 服务（`BindAddress: \"0\"`），禁用 health probe（`HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\"`）\n36:    - 注册 Reconciler 并启动 Manager，监听 `ctrl.SetupSignalHandler()` 实现优雅关闭\n37: \n38: 4. **常量定义**\n39:    - `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`：空闲过期阈值\n40: \n41: 5. **单元测试**\n42:    - Sandbox 不存在时返回空结果（NotFound 处理）\n43:    - 缺少 `last-activity-time` 注解时不删除、不 requeue\n44:    - 注解值非 RFC3339 格式时返回错误 + 30s requeue\n45:    - 未过期时返回正确 `RequeueAfter`\n46:    - 已过期时触发 Delete 调用\n47:    - Delete 返回 NotFound 时视为成功\n48: \n49: ### 不包含\n50: \n51: - TTL（最大存活时间）清理：由 WorkloadManager 的 `LifecycleManager` 负责\n52: - 孤儿 CR 清理：由 WorkloadManager 的 `LifecycleManager` 负责\n53: - Store（Redis）交互：agentd 不依赖 Store，仅读取 Sandbox CR 注解\n54: - Sandbox 创建/更新逻辑：由 WorkloadManager 负责\n55: - 自定义闲置阈值：固定使用 `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15min`，不从 CR Spec 读取\n56: - Metrics / Health Probe：本控制器禁用这些端点（S 级简化）\n57: \n58: ## 架构概要\n59: \n60: ### 组件关系\n61: \n62: ```\n63: Kubernetes API Server\n64:     │\n65:     ├── watch Sandbox CR (agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1)\n66:     │       │\n67:     │       ▼\n68:     │   agentd Reconciler\n69:     │       │\n70:     │       ├── 读取 annotation: last-activity-time\n71:     │       ├── 计算: expirationTime = lastActivity + 15min\n72:     │       ├── 未过期 → RequeueAfter(time.Until(expirationTime))\n73:     │       └── 已过期 → Delete(Sandbox)\n74:     │\n75:     └── WorkloadManager LifecycleManager（独立运行，负责 TTL/孤儿清理）\n76:             │\n77:             └── 轮询 Redis Store → 清理过期沙箱\n78: ```\n79: \n80: ### 目录结构\n81: \n82: ```\n83: cmd/agentd/\n84: └── main.go           — Binary 入口：Scheme 注册、Manager 构造、启动\n85: pkg/agentd/\n86: ├── reconciler.go     — Reconciler 结构体 + Reconcile 方法\n87: ├── reconciler_test.go — 单元测试\n88: └── const.go          — SessionExpirationTimeout 常量\n89: ```\n90: \n91: ### Reconcile 算法\n92: \n93: ```\n94: 1. Get Sandbox by req.NamespacedName\n95: 2. If NotFound → return (Result{}, nil)\n96: 3. If other error → return (Result{}, err)\n97: 4. Read annotation \"last-activity-time\"\n98: 5. If missing or empty → return (Result{}, nil)\n99: 6. Parse as RFC3339\n100:    - If parse error → return (Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)\n101: 7. expirationTime = lastActivity + 15min\n102: 8. If now.After(expirationTime):\n103:      Delete(sandbox)\n104:      - If NotFound → return (Result{}, nil)\n105:      - If error → return (Result{}, err)\n106:      - Else → return (Result{}, nil)\n107: 9. Else:\n108:      return (Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil)\n109: ```\n110: \n111: ## 影响分析\n112: \n113: ### 直接影响\n114: \n115: | 组件 | 影响 | 说明 |\n116: |------|------|------|\n117: | `cmd/agentd/main.go` | 新增 | Binary 入口 |\n118: | `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` | 新增 | Reconciler 实现 |\n119: | `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go` | 新增 | 单元测试 |\n120: | `pkg/agentd/const.go` | 新增 | 常量定义 |\n121: | `go.mod` | 修改 | 新增 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime`、`sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` 依赖 |\n122: \n123: ### 上游依赖（本变更依赖的已完成组件）\n124: \n125: | 组件 | 依赖关系 |\n126: |------|----------|\n127: | `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | controller-runtime 框架（Manager、Reconciler 模式） |\n128: | `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1` | Sandbox CRD 类型定义 |\n129: | `pkg/workloadmanager` | 仅引用 `LastActivityAnnotationKey` 常量 |\n130: | `k8s.io/apimachinery` | errors.IsNotFound、runtime.Scheme 等 |\n131: \n132: ### 下游依赖（本变更完成后解锁）\n133: \n134: | 组件 | 依赖关系 |\n135: |------|----------|\n136: | 集群运维 | 可部署 agentd Deployment 实现原生 K8s 空闲清理 |\n137: | WorkloadManager | 可与 LifecycleManager 共存，形成双层清理保障 |\n138: \n139: ### 无影响的组件\n140: \n141: - `pkg/router/` — 仅写入 `last-activity-time` 注解，不依赖 agentd\n142: - `pkg/workloadmanager/` — 独立运行，清理逻辑不受 agentd 影响\n143: - `pkg/apis/` — CRD 类型定义独立\n144: - `client-go/` — 生成代码不涉及 agentd\n145: - `pkg/picod/` — 沙箱内守护进程，不感知清理控制器\n146: \n147: ### 风险评估\n148: \n149: | 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n150: |------|------|----------|\n151: | controller-runtime 依赖引入增加构建体积 | 低 | 仅 agentd binary 受影响，其他组件不变 |\n152: | 与 LifecycleManager 重复删除 | 低 | Delete 是幂等操作，API Server 返回 NotFound 时双方均视为成功 |\n153: | 注解格式异常导致 reconcile 错误 | 低 | 解析错误返回 30s requeue，不会阻塞其他 Sandbox |\n154: | 大量 Sandbox 同时过期导致 API Server 压力 | 低 | controller-runtime 的 workqueue 有速率限制；S 级规模场景可控 |\n155: | agentd 未部署时清理回退到 LifecycleManager | 无风险 | LifecycleManager 始终运行，agentd 为增强而非替代 |\n156: \n157: ### 与现有组件的交互\n158: \n159: | 组件 | 交互方式 | 影响 |\n160: |------|----------|------|\n161: | Router | 在代理请求时更新 Sandbox 的 `last-activity-time` 注解 | 无影响。Router 不感知 agentd 存在 |\n162: | WorkloadManager | 创建 Sandbox 时设置 `last-activity-time` 注解 | 无影响。WorkloadManager 已有此逻辑 |\n163: | LifecycleManager | 独立轮询 Store 清理过期沙箱 | 互补关系：agentd 基于 K8s watch，LifecycleManager 基于 Store 轮询 |\n164: \n165: ## 备选方案\n166: \n167: ### 1. 独立 controller-runtime 控制器（✅ 选定方案）\n168: \n169: **做法**：新建 `pkg/agentd` 包，使用 controller-runtime 框架 watch Sandbox CR，基于 `last-activity-time` 注解触发删除。\n170: \n171: **优点**：\n172: - 利用 K8s 原生 watch 机制，无需轮询，延迟低\n173: - 不依赖外部 Store（Redis），减少故障面\n174: - controller-runtime 提供成熟的 workqueue、重试、leader election 等基础设施\n175: - 与 LifecycleManager 形成双层保障，互不干扰\n176: \n177: **缺点**：\n178: - 引入 controller-runtime 依赖，增加构建体积\n179: - 需要独立部署 agentd Deployment\n180: \n181: **决策**：采用。符合 Kubernetes Operator 最佳实践，变更范围可控（S 级），与现有架构互补。\n182: \n183: ### 2. 扩展 LifecycleManager 增加 watch 模式\n184: \n185: **做法**：在现有 `LifecycleManager` 中添加 informer watch，替代轮询逻辑。\n186: \n187: **优点**：无需新增 binary，复用现有部署  \n188: **缺点**：LifecycleManager 职责膨胀（当前负责 TTL/孤儿/幽灵清理 + Store 交互），混合 watch 和轮询两种模式增加复杂度；改动范围超出 S 级  \n189: **决策**：不采用。单一职责原则，watch 模式更适合独立控制器。\n190: \n191: ### 3. Kubernetes TTL Controller（`ttlSecondsAfterFinished`）\n192: \n193: **做法**：利用 K8s 原生 TTL 机制，在 Sandbox 上设置 `ttlSecondsAfterFinished`。\n194: \n195: **优点**：无需自定义控制器，K8s 原生支持  \n196: **缺点**：TTL 从资源创建/完成时间开始计算，无法基于\"最后活动时间\"动态更新；不满足空闲检测需求  \n197: **决策**：不采用。业务需求是基于活动时间的空闲检测，非固定 TTL。\n198: \n199: ### 4. CronJob 定期清理\n200: \n201: **做法**：部署 CronJob 定期扫描 Sandbox 注解并删除过期资源。\n202: \n203: **优点**：实现简单，无需常驻进程  \n204: **缺点**：清理延迟取决于 CronJob 周期；无法实现精确的过期时间点触发；扫描全量 Sandbox 效率低  \n205: **决策**：不采用。watch 模式更高效、延迟更低。\n206: \n207: ## 实现要点\n208: \n209: 1. **常量定义**：`SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`，与 LifecycleManager 的 `DefaultIdleTimeout` 保持一致\n210: 2. **注解引用**：使用 `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey`（值为 `\"last-activity-time\"`），避免魔法字符串\n211: 3. **时间解析**：严格使用 `time.RFC3339` 格式，解析失败返回错误 + 30s requeue\n212: 4. **Delete 幂等**：`errors.IsNotFound(err)` 时视为成功，返回 `(Result{}, nil)`\n213: 5. **Requeue 精度**：未过期时 `RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)`，确保在过期时刻精确触发\n214: 6. **Scheme 注册**：`sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder)` + `scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder)`（core 类型）\n215: 7. **Manager 配置**：禁用 metrics 和 health probe（`BindAddress: \"0\"`），最小化资源占用\n216: \n217: ## 验收标准\n218: \n219: 1. **Reconciler 行为**\n220:    - [ ] Sandbox 不存在时返回 `(Result{}, nil)`\n221:    - [ ] 缺少 `last-activity-time` 注解时不删除、不 requeue\n222:    - [ ] 注解为空字符串时不删除、不 requeue\n223:    - [ ] 注解值非 RFC3339 格式时返回错误 + `RequeueAfter: 30s`\n224:    - [ ] 未过期时返回 `RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)`\n225:    - [ ] 已过期时调用 `Delete` 删除 Sandbox\n226:    - [ ] Delete 返回 NotFound 时视为成功\n227: \n228: 2. **Manager 配置**\n229:    - [ ] Scheme 包含 core 类型和 `sandboxv1alpha1`\n230:    - [ ] Metrics 服务禁用（`BindAddress: \"0\"`）\n231:    - [ ] Health Probe 禁用（`HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\"`）\n232:    - [ ] 信号处理实现优雅关闭\n233: \n234: 3. **测试覆盖**\n235:    - [ ] `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` 全部通过\n236:    - [ ] 使用 fake client 模拟所有 reconcile 分支\n237:    - [ ] 覆盖 Get NotFound、注解缺失、解析错误、未过期、已过期、Delete NotFound 场景\n238: \n239: 4. **代码质量**\n240:    - [ ] `go vet ./pkg/agentd/...` 无告警\n241:    - [ ] `go mod tidy` 后无未使用依赖\n242: \n243: ## 状态\n244: \n245: - [ ] 提案审查\n246: - [ ] 实现\n247: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 247 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n\n**Module:** pkg/agentd\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** S\n\n## 目的\n\n为 AgentCube 实现一个独立的 `agentd` 组件，基于 controller-runtime 构建 Sandbox 资源的空闲清理控制器。当 Sandbox 的 `last-activity-time` 注解标识的最后活动时间超过 15 分钟（`SessionExpirationTimeout`）时，控制器自动删除该 Sandbox，释放集群资源。\n\n当前沙箱的空闲清理逻辑由 WorkloadManager 的 `LifecycleManager` 通过轮询 Store（Redis）实现，存在以下局限：\n- 依赖外部 Store，Store 不可用时清理失效\n- 轮询间隔（默认 5 分钟）导致清理延迟\n- 无法利用 Kubernetes 原生 watch 机制实时响应 Sandbox 状态变化\n\n`agentd` 作为独立的 in-cluster 控制器，直接 watch Sandbox CR 的创建/更新事件，通过 requeue 机制在精确的过期时间点触发删除，提供更可靠、低延迟的空闲清理能力。\n\n## 范围\n\n### 包含","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775847757227,"end":1775847757240}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847758508,"sessionID":"ses_28739d782ffesMLvrTsRXAlpsf","part":{"id":"prt_d78c65634001fWBT1n4iglJ1dJ","messageID":"msg_d78c64252001zYCgDHqNC1DMkv","sessionID":"ses_28739d782ffesMLvrTsRXAlpsf","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_d73d168c445144fd8bb42c44","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 — Design\n2: \n3: ## 1. Architecture\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 Purpose\n6: \n7: 实现一个独立的 `agentd` 组件，作为基于 controller-runtime 的 Kubernetes 控制器，负责 watch `Sandbox` CR（`agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`）并根据 `last-activity-time` 注解自动清理空闲沙箱。与 WorkloadManager 的 `LifecycleManager`（基于 Redis Store 轮询）形成双层清理保障，提供更可靠、低延迟的空闲检测能力。\n8: \n9: ### 1.2 Package Layout\n10: \n11: ```\n12: cmd/agentd/\n13: └── main.go              — Binary 入口：Scheme 注册、Manager 构造、启动\n14: pkg/agentd/\n15: ├── reconciler.go        — Reconciler 结构体 + Reconcile + SetupWithManager\n16: ├── reconciler_test.go   — 单元测试（fake client）\n17: └── const.go             — SessionExpirationTimeout 常量\n18: pkg/workloadmanager/\n19: └── const.go             — LastActivityAnnotationKey 常量（新增）\n20: ```\n21: \n22: ### 1.3 Data Flow\n23: \n24: ```\n25: Kubernetes API Server\n26:     │\n27:     ├── Sandbox Create/Update/Delete Event\n28:     │       │\n29:     │       ▼\n30:     │   controller-runtime Informer (cache)\n31:     │       │\n32:     │       ▼\n33:     │   Reconciler.Reconcile(ctx, req)\n34:     │       │\n35:     │       ├── 1. Get Sandbox by NamespacedName\n36:     │       │       ├── NotFound → return (Result{}, nil)\n37:     │       │       └── Error  → return (Result{}, err)\n38:     │       │\n39:     │       ├── 2. Read annotation \"last-activity-time\"\n40:     │       │       └── Missing/empty → return (Result{}, nil)\n41:     │       │\n42:     │       ├── 3. Parse RFC3339 timestamp\n43:     │       │       └── Parse error → return (Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)\n44:     │       │\n45:     │       ├── 4. Compute expirationTime = lastActivity + 15min\n46:     │       │\n47:     │       └── 5. Check expiration\n48:     │               ├── now.After(expirationTime)\n49:     │               │       ├── Delete(sandbox)\n50:     │               │       │       ├── NotFound → return (Result{}, nil)\n51:     │               │       │       ├── Error    → return (Result{}, err)\n52:     │               │       │       └── Success  → return (Result{}, nil)\n53:     │               │\n54:     │               └── !now.After(expirationTime)\n55:     │                       └── return (Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil)\n56:     │\n57:     └── WorkloadManager LifecycleManager（独立运行，负责 TTL/孤儿/幽灵清理）\n58: ```\n59: \n60: ### 1.4 Dependencies\n61: \n62: | Dependency | Purpose | Type |\n63: |---|---|---|\n64: | `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | Manager、Reconciler 模式、workqueue | Direct |\n65: | `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1` | Sandbox CRD 类型定义 | Direct |\n66: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors` | `errors.IsNotFound` 判断 | Direct |\n67: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime` | Scheme 注册 | Direct |\n68: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/util/runtime` | `utilruntime.Must` 安全初始化 | Direct |\n69: | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager` | `LastActivityAnnotationKey` 常量引用 | Internal |\n70: \n71: ## 2. Data Structures\n72: \n73: ### 2.1 Constants\n74: \n75: ```go\n76: // pkg/agentd/const.go\n77: package agentd\n78: \n79: import \"time\"\n80: \n81: // SessionExpirationTimeout is the fixed idle expiration threshold.\n82: // A Sandbox is considered expired when its last activity time plus\n83: // this duration has elapsed.\n84: var SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n85: ```\n86: \n87: ```go\n88: // pkg/workloadmanager/const.go (new file)\n89: package workloadmanager\n90: \n91: // LastActivityAnnotationKey is the annotation key used to store the\n92: // last activity timestamp on Sandbox objects. The value is an RFC3339\n93: // formatted timestamp updated by the Router on each proxied request.\n94: const LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"\n95: ```\n96: \n97: ### 2.2 Reconciler\n98: \n99: ```go\n100: // pkg/agentd/reconciler.go\n101: package agentd\n102: \n103: import (\n104:     \"context\"\n105:     \"time\"\n106: \n107:     sandboxv1alpha1 \"sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1\"\n108:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors\"\n109:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n110:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime\"\n111:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client\"\n112: )\n113: \n114: // Reconciler implements the idle cleanup controller for Sandbox resources.\n115: // It embeds client.Client for API server operations and holds a Scheme\n116: // for type registration.\n117: type Reconciler struct {\n118:     client.Client\n119:     Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n120: }\n121: ```\n122: \n123: ### 2.3 Sentinel Errors\n124: \n125: 无自定义 sentinel errors。所有错误来源于：\n126: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors.IsNotFound(err)` — 资源不存在\n127: - `time.Parse` 返回的解析错误 — 时间戳格式非法\n128: - controller-runtime 返回的网络/API 错误 — 重试由框架处理\n129: \n130: ### 2.4 Key Constants Reference\n131: \n132: | Constant | Value | Defined In | Used By |\n133: |---|---|---|---|\n134: | `SessionExpirationTimeout` | `15 * time.Minute` | `pkg/agentd/const.go` | `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` |\n135: | `LastActivityAnnotationKey` | `\"last-activity-time\"` | `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go` | `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go`, `pkg/router/`, `pkg/workloadmanager/` |\n136: \n137: ## 3. API Contracts\n138: \n139: 本控制器不暴露 HTTP API。与 Kubernetes API Server 的交互通过 controller-runtime client 完成。\n140: \n141: ### 3.1 Watched Resources\n142: \n143: | API Group | Version | Kind | Trigger |\n144: |---|---|---|---|\n145: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `v1alpha1` | `Sandbox` | Create, Update, Delete（controller-runtime `For()` 默认行为） |\n146: \n147: ### 3.2 Reconcile Contract\n148: \n149: **Input:** `ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request`\n150: \n151: **Output:** `(ctrl.Result, error)`\n152: \n153: | Condition | Result | Error | Side Effect |\n154: |---|---|---|---|\n155: | Sandbox NotFound | `{}` | `nil` | None |\n156: | Get error (non-NotFound) | `{}` | `err` | None (retry) |\n157: | Annotation missing/empty | `{}` | `nil` | None |\n158: | Timestamp parse error | `{RequeueAfter: 30s}` | `err` | None (retry) |\n159: | Not expired | `{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}` | `nil` | None |\n160: | Expired, Delete NotFound | `{}` | `nil` | None (already deleted) |\n161: | Expired, Delete error | `{}` | `err` | None (retry) |\n162: | Expired, Delete success | `{}` | `nil` | Sandbox deleted |\n163: \n164: ### 3.3 Manager Configuration\n165: \n166: | Option | Value | Rationale |\n167: |---|---|---|\n168: | `Scheme` | core + `sandboxv1alpha1` | 支持 Sandbox 类型操作 |\n169: | `Metrics.BindAddress` | `\"0\"` | S 级简化，禁用 metrics 服务 |\n170: | `HealthProbeBindAddress` | `\"0\"` | S 级简化，禁用 health probe |\n171: | Signal handler | `ctrl.SetupSignalHandler()` | SIGTERM/SIGINT 优雅关闭 |\n172: \n173: ## 4. Core Implementation\n174: \n175: ### 4.1 Reconcile Method\n176: \n177: ```go\n178: func (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error) {\n179:     sandbox := &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}\n180:     if err := r.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox); err != nil {\n181:         if errors.IsNotFound(err) {\n182:             return ctrl.Result{}, nil\n183:         }\n184:         return ctrl.Result{}, err\n185:     }\n186: \n187:     lastActivityStr, exists := sandbox.Annotations[workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey]\n188:     if !exists || lastActivityStr == \"\" {\n189:         return ctrl.Result{}, nil\n190:     }\n191: \n192:     lastActivity, err := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)\n193:     if err != nil {\n194:         return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30 * time.Second}, err\n195:     }\n196: \n197:     expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)\n198: \n199:     if time.Now().After(expirationTime) {\n200:         if err := r.Delete(ctx, sandbox); err != nil && !errors.IsNotFound(err) {\n201:             return ctrl.Result{}, err\n202:         }\n203:         return ctrl.Result{}, nil\n204:     }\n205: \n206:     return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil\n207: }\n208: ```\n209: \n210: ### 4.2 SetupWithManager\n211: \n212: ```go\n213: func (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error {\n214:     return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n215:         For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n216:         Complete(r)\n217: }\n218: ```\n219: \n220: ### 4.3 Binary Entry Point\n221: \n222: ```go\n223: // cmd/agentd/main.go\n224: package main\n225: \n226: import (\n227:     \"flag\"\n228:     \"os\"\n229: \n230:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n231:     utilruntime \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/util/runtime\"\n232:     sandboxv1alpha1 \"sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1\"\n233:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime\"\n234:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/log/zap\"\n235:     metricsserver \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/metrics/server\"\n236: \n237:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd\"\n238: )\n239: \n240: var schemeBuilder = runtime.NewScheme()\n241: \n242: func init() {\n243:     utilruntime.Must(scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n244:     utilruntime.Must(sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n245: }\n246: \n247: func main() {\n248:     opts := zap.Options{\n249:         Development: true,\n250:     }\n251:     opts.BindFlags(flag.CommandLine)\n252:     flag.Parse()\n253: \n254:     ctrl.SetLogger(zap.New(zap.UseFlagOptions(&opts)))\n255: \n256:     mgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{\n257:         Scheme:                 schemeBuilder,\n258:         Metrics:                metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"},\n259:         HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\",\n260:     })\n261:     if err != nil {\n262:         setupLog.Error(err, \"unable to start manager\")\n263:         os.Exit(1)\n264:     }\n265: \n266:     if err := (&agentd.Reconciler{\n267:         Client: mgr.GetClient(),\n268:         Scheme: mgr.GetScheme(),\n269:     }).SetupWithManager(mgr); err != nil {\n270:         setupLog.Error(err, \"unable to create controller\", \"controller\", \"Sandbox\")\n271:         os.Exit(1)\n272:     }\n273: \n274:     setupLog.Info(\"starting manager\")\n275:     if err := mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler()); err != nil {\n276:         setupLog.Error(err, \"problem running manager\")\n277:         os.Exit(1)\n278:     }\n279: }\n280: \n281: var setupLog = ctrl.Log.WithName(\"setup\")\n282: ```\n283: \n284: ### 4.4 Reconcile Decision Tree\n285: \n286: ```\n287: Reconcile(ctx, req)\n288: ├── Get(req.NamespacedName)\n289: │   ├── NotFound → return ({}, nil)          [已删除，无需处理]\n290: │   └── Error    → return ({}, err)           [API 错误，重试]\n291: │\n292: ├── Annotations[LastActivityAnnotationKey]\n293: │   ├── Missing   → return ({}, nil)          [无活动时间，跳过]\n294: │   └── Empty     → return ({}, nil)          [空值，跳过]\n295: │\n296: ├── time.Parse(RFC3339, value)\n297: │   └── Error → return ({RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)  [格式异常，30s 后重试]\n298: │\n299: ├── expirationTime = lastActivity + 15min\n300: │\n301: └── time.Now().After(expirationTime)\n302:     ├── true (expired)\n303:     │   └── Delete(sandbox)\n304:     │       ├── NotFound → return ({}, nil)   [已被其他控制器删除]\n305:     │       ├── Error    → return ({}, err)    [删除失败，重试]\n306:     │       └── Success  → return ({}, nil)    [删除成功]\n307:     │\n308:     └── false (not expired)\n309:         └── return ({RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil)\n310: ```\n311: \n312: ### 4.5 Time Precision Considerations\n313: \n314: - `time.Until(expirationTime)` 返回 `time.Duration`，在过期时刻临近时趋近于 0\n315: - controller-runtime 对 `RequeueAfter: 0` 的处理等同于立即 requeue，不会导致 busy loop\n316: - 当 `time.Now()` 恰好等于 `expirationTime` 时，`After()` 返回 `false`，下一次 requeue 会在下一个调度周期触发\n317: \n318: ## 5. Error Handling\n319: \n320: ### 5.1 Error Classification\n321: \n322: | Error Source | Error Type | Handling Strategy |\n323: |---|---|---|\n324: | `r.Get` — NotFound | `apierrors.IsNotFound` | 静默返回 `({}, nil)`，不重试 |\n325: | `r.Get` — 其他 | Network/API error | 返回 `({}, err)`，controller-runtime workqueue 指数退避重试 |\n326: | `time.Parse` | Format error | 返回 `({RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)`，固定 30s 后重试 |\n327: | `r.Delete` — NotFound | `apierrors.IsNotFound` | 静默返回 `({}, nil)`，幂等处理 |\n328: | `r.Delete` — 其他 | Network/API error | 返回 `({}, err)`，controller-runtime workqueue 指数退避重试 |\n329: \n330: ### 5.2 Idempotency Guarantees\n331: \n332: - **Delete 幂等**：多次调用 `Delete` 对同一 Sandbox 不会产生副作用，`IsNotFound` 视为成功\n333: - **Reconcile 幂等**：同一 Sandbox 的多次 reconcile 调用不会产生重复删除\n334: - **与 LifecycleManager 共存**：两者可能同时尝试删除同一 Sandbox，`IsNotFound` 处理确保双方均正常完成\n335: \n336: ### 5.3 Error Propagation\n337: \n338: - 解析错误（`time.Parse`）返回给 controller-runtime，记录到日志但不会导致控制器崩溃\n339: - API 错误由 controller-runtime 的 workqueue 管理重试，自动指数退避\n340: - 不会 panic，所有错误路径都有明确的返回值\n341: \n342: ## 6. Testing Strategy\n343: \n344: ### 6.1 Unit Test Matrix\n345: \n346: | Test Case | Sandbox Exists | Annotation | Timestamp | Time vs Expiration | Expected Result |\n347: |---|---|---|---|---|---|\n348: | `TestReconcile_SandboxNotFound` | No (Get NotFound) | — | — | — | `Result{}`, `nil` |\n349: | `TestReconcile_GetError` | No (Get error) | — | — | — | `Result{}`, `err` |\n350: | `TestReconcile_AnnotationMissing` | Yes | Missing | — | — | `Result{}`, `nil` |\n351: | `TestReconcile_AnnotationEmpty` | Yes | `\"\"` | — | — | `Result{}`, `nil` |\n352: | `TestReconcile_InvalidTimestamp` | Yes | `\"not-a-timestamp\"` | Parse fails | — | `Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}`, `err` |\n353: | `TestReconcile_NotExpired` | Yes | Valid RFC3339 | 5 min ago | `now < expiration` | `Result{RequeueAfter: ~10m}`, `nil` |\n354: | `TestReconcile_Expired` | Yes | Valid RFC3339 | 20 min ago | `now > expiration` | Delete called, `Result{}`, `nil` |\n355: | `TestReconcile_DeleteNotFound` | Yes (Delete NotFound) | Valid RFC3339 | 20 min ago | `now > expiration` | `Result{}`, `nil` |\n356: | `TestReconcile_DeleteError` | Yes (Delete error) | Valid RFC3339 | 20 min ago | `now > expiration` | `Result{}`, `err` |\n357: | `TestReconcile_AtExpirationBoundary` | Yes | Valid RFC3339 | Exactly 15 min ago | `now == expiration` | `Result{RequeueAfter: >=0}`, `nil` |\n358: \n359: ### 6.2 Test Helpers\n360: \n361: ```go\n362: // 使用 controller-runtime fake client\n363: import (\n364:     \"context\"\n365:     \"testing\"\n366:     \"time\"\n367: \n368:     \"github.com/stretchr/testify/assert\"\n369:     \"github.com/stretchr/testify/require\"\n370:     sandboxv1alpha1 \"sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1\"\n371:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors\"\n372:     metav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n373:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n374:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/types\"\n375:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client/fake\"\n376:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/reconcile\"\n377: \n378:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd\"\n379:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager\"\n380: )\n381: \n382: func newTestScheme() *runtime.Scheme {\n383:     scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n384:     _ = sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(scheme)\n385:     return scheme\n386: }\n387: \n388: func newFakeReconciler(objects ...runtime.Object) *agentd.Reconciler {\n389:     return &agentd.Reconciler{\n390:         Client: fake.NewClientBuilder().\n391:             WithScheme(newTestScheme()).\n392:             WithRuntimeObjects(objects...).\n393:             Build(),\n394:         Scheme: newTestScheme(),\n395:     }\n396: }\n397: \n398: func newSandbox(ns, name string, annotations map[string]string) *sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox {\n399:     return &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{\n400:         ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n401:             Namespace:   ns,\n402:             Name:        name,\n403:             Annotations: annotations,\n404:         },\n405:     }\n406: }\n407: ```\n408: \n409: ### 6.3 Mock Strategy\n410: \n411: - **Fake Client**：使用 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client/fake` 模拟 Kubernetes API Server\n412: - **时间控制**：测试中通过构造不同的 `last-activity-time` 值和依赖 `time.Now()` 的相对计算来覆盖过期/未过期分支\n413: - **Error Injection**：fake client 不支持直接注入 Get/Delete 错误，可通过自定义 `client.Client` wrapper 或使用 `WithStatusSubresource` 等 builder 选项模拟\n414: \n415: ### 6.4 Test File Structure\n416: \n417: ```go\n418: // pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go\n419: \n420: func TestReconcile_SandboxNotFound(t *testing.T) { ... }\n421: func TestReconcile_GetError(t *testing.T) { ... }\n422: func TestReconcile_AnnotationMissing(t *testing.T) { ... }\n423: func TestReconcile_AnnotationEmpty(t *testing.T) { ... }\n424: func TestReconcile_InvalidTimestamp(t *testing.T) { ... }\n425: func TestReconcile_NotExpired(t *testing.T) { ... }\n426: func TestReconcile_Expired(t *testing.T) { ... }\n427: func TestReconcile_DeleteNotFound(t *testing.T) { ... }\n428: func TestReconcile_DeleteError(t *testing.T) { ... }\n429: func TestReconcile_AtExpirationBoundary(t *testing.T) { ... }\n430: \n431: func TestSetupWithManager(t *testing.T) { ... }\n432: ```\n433: \n434: ### 6.5 Gate Requirements\n435: \n436: - `go vet ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` — 无告警\n437: - `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` — 全部通过\n438: - `go mod tidy` — 无变更\n439: \n440: ## 7. Deployment Considerations\n441: \n442: ### 7.1 Deployment Manifest\n443: \n444: agentd 作为独立的 Deployment 部署在集群中：\n445: \n446: ```yaml\n447: apiVersion: apps/v1\n448: kind: Deployment\n449: metadata:\n450:   name: agentd\n451:   namespace: agentcube-system\n452: spec:\n453:   replicas: 1\n454:   selector:\n455:     matchLabels:\n456:       app: agentd\n457:   template:\n458:     metadata:\n459:       labels:\n460:         app: agentd\n461:     spec:\n462:       serviceAccountName: agentd\n463:       containers:\n464:       - name: agentd\n465:         image: agentcube/agentd:latest\n466:         resources:\n467:           requests:\n468:             cpu: 50m\n469:             memory: 64Mi\n470:           limits:\n471:             cpu: 200m\n472:             memory: 128Mi\n473: ---\n474: apiVersion: v1\n475: kind: ServiceAccount\n476: metadata:\n477:   name: agentd\n478:   namespace: agentcube-system\n479: ---\n480: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n481: kind: ClusterRole\n482: metadata:\n483:   name: agentd\n484: rules:\n485: - apiGroups: [\"agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n486:   resources: [\"sandboxes\"]\n487:   verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"delete\"]\n488: ---\n489: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n490: kind: ClusterRoleBinding\n491: metadata:\n492:   name: agentd\n493: roleRef:\n494:   apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n495:   kind: ClusterRole\n496:   name: agentd\n497: subjects:\n498: - kind: ServiceAccount\n499:   name: agentd\n500:   namespace: agentcube-system\n501: ```\n502: \n503: ### 7.2 RBAC Requirements\n504: \n505: | API Group | Resource | Verbs | Purpose |\n506: |---|---|---|---|\n507: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxes` | `get`, `list`, `watch` | 读取 Sandbox 状态和注解 |\n508: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxes` | `delete` | 删除过期 Sandbox |\n509: \n510: ### 7.3 Resource Requirements\n511: \n512: | Resource | Request | Limit | Rationale |\n513: |---|---|---|---|\n514: | CPU | 50m | 200m | 控制器轻量，仅在事件触发时工作 |\n515: | Memory | 64Mi | 128Mi | controller-runtime informer cache 占用 |\n516: \n517: ### 7.4 Coexistence with LifecycleManager\n518: \n519: | Aspect | agentd | LifecycleManager |\n520: |---|---|---|\n521: | Trigger | K8s watch (event-driven) | Polling Redis Store (5min interval) |\n522: | Data Source | Sandbox CR annotations | Redis Store entries |\n523: | Cleanup Scope | Idle only (15min) | TTL + Idle + Orphan + Ghost |\n524: | Delete Idempotency | `IsNotFound` → success | `IsNotFound` → success |\n525: | Failure Mode | Falls back to LifecycleManager | Falls back to agentd |\n526: \n527: 两者互补运行，互不依赖，Delete 操作天然幂等。\n528: \n529: ## 8. Implementation Steps\n530: \n531: ### Phase 1: 常量定义\n532: \n533: - [ ] 创建 `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go`，定义 `LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"`\n534: - [ ] 创建 `pkg/agentd/const.go`，定义 `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`\n535: \n536: ### Phase 2: Reconciler 实现\n537: \n538: - [ ] 创建 `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go`\n539: - [ ] 实现 `Reconciler` 结构体（嵌入 `client.Client` + `*runtime.Scheme`）\n540: - [ ] 实现 `Reconcile` 方法（完整算法）\n541: - [ ] 实现 `SetupWithManager` 方法\n542: \n543: ### Phase 3: Binary Entry Point\n544: \n545: - [ ] 创建 `cmd/agentd/main.go`\n546: - [ ] Scheme 注册（core + `sandboxv1alpha1`）\n547: - [ ] Manager 构造（禁用 metrics/health probe）\n548: - [ ] Reconciler 注册 + Start\n549: \n550: ### Phase 4: 单元测试\n551: \n552: - [ ] 创建 `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go`\n553: - [ ] 实现所有测试用例（见 6.1 测试矩阵）\n554: - [ ] 验证 `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` 全部通过\n555: \n556: ### Phase 5: 代码质量门禁\n557: \n558: - [ ] `go vet ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` 无告警\n559: - [ ] `go mod tidy` 无变更\n560: - [ ] 验收标准对照检查（见 proposal.md 验收标准）\n561: \n562: ## 9. Future Changes\n563: \n564: - **可配置过期阈值**：当前固定 15 分钟，未来可从 ConfigMap 或 Sandbox annotation 读取自定义阈值\n565: - **Metrics 集成**：启用 metrics 服务，暴露 `agentd_sandboxes_cleaned_total`、`agentd_reconcile_duration_seconds` 等指标\n566: - **Leader Election**：多副本部署时启用 controller-runtime leader election，避免重复删除\n567: - **Grace Period**：删除前添加宽限期，允许 Sandbox 内进程完成清理\n568: - **Event Recording**：删除 Sandbox 时记录 Kubernetes Event，便于审计和调试\n569: - **Finalizer 支持**：在删除前执行自定义清理逻辑（如清理关联的 ConfigMap/Secret）\n\n(End of file - total 569 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 — Design\n\n## 1. Architecture\n\n### 1.1 Purpose\n\n实现一个独立的 `agentd` 组件，作为基于 controller-runtime 的 Kubernetes 控制器，负责 watch `Sandbox` CR（`agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`）并根据 `last-activity-time` 注解自动清理空闲沙箱。与 WorkloadManager 的 `LifecycleManager`（基于 Redis Store 轮询）形成双层清理保障，提供更可靠、低延迟的空闲检测能力。\n\n### 1.2 Package Layout\n\n```\ncmd/agentd/\n└── main.go              — Binary 入口：Scheme 注册、Manager 构造、启动\npkg/agentd/\n├── reconciler.go        — Reconciler 结构体 + Reconcile + SetupWithManager\n├── reconciler_test.go   — 单元测试（fake client）\n└── const.go             — SessionExpirationTimeout 常量\npkg/workloadmanager/\n└── const.go             — LastActivityAnnotationKey 常量（新增）\n```","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/design.md","time":{"start":1775847758497,"end":1775847758506}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847759861,"sessionID":"ses_28739d782ffesMLvrTsRXAlpsf","part":{"id":"prt_d78c65b2500135x5HXAMELge1N","messageID":"msg_d78c64252001zYCgDHqNC1DMkv","sessionID":"ses_28739d782ffesMLvrTsRXAlpsf","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_d0f82914145c4bb499cfc761","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** pkg/agentd\n4: > **Language:** Go\n5: > **Size:** S\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-018/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-018/design.md`, `changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md`\n8: \n9: ## T1. 定义常量 — pkg/workloadmanager/const.go\n10: \n11: - [ ] 1.1 创建 `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go`\n12: - [ ] 1.2 定义 `LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"`\n13: - [ ] 1.3 运行 `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 确认编译通过\n14: \n15: **Verification:** `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go` 存在；`LastActivityAnnotationKey` 值为 `\"last-activity-time\"`；编译零错误\n16: \n17: ---\n18: \n19: ## T2. 定义常量 — pkg/agentd/const.go\n20: \n21: - [ ] 2.1 创建 `pkg/agentd/` 目录\n22: - [ ] 2.2 创建 `pkg/agentd/const.go`\n23: - [ ] 2.3 定义 `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`（带注释说明用途）\n24: - [ ] 2.4 运行 `go build ./pkg/agentd/...` 确认编译通过\n25: \n26: **Verification:** `pkg/agentd/const.go` 存在；`SessionExpirationTimeout` 值为 `15 * time.Minute`；编译零错误\n27: \n28: ---\n29: \n30: ## T3. 实现 Reconciler 结构体和 Reconcile 方法\n31: \n32: - [ ] 3.1 创建 `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go`\n33: - [ ] 3.2 导入依赖：`context`, `time`, `sandboxv1alpha1`（`sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`）, `errors`（`k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors`）, `runtime`（`k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime`）, `ctrl`（`sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime`）, `client`（`sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client`）, `workloadmanager`（内部包）\n34: - [ ] 3.3 定义 `Reconciler` 结构体，嵌入 `client.Client`，字段 `Scheme *runtime.Scheme`\n35: - [ ] 3.4 实现 `Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error)` 方法，完整算法：\n36:   - `sandbox := &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}`；`r.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox)`\n37:   - `errors.IsNotFound(err)` → `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n38:   - 其他 Get 错误 → `return ctrl.Result{}, err`\n39:   - 读取 `sandbox.Annotations[workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey]`\n40:   - 注解缺失或为空 → `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n41:   - `time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)`，解析错误 → `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err`\n42:   - `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`\n43:   - `time.Now().After(expirationTime)` 为 true：\n44:     - `r.Delete(ctx, sandbox)`，错误且非 `IsNotFound` → `return ctrl.Result{}, err`\n45:     - `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n46:   - 否则 → `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil`\n47: - [ ] 3.5 运行 `go build ./pkg/agentd/...` 确认编译通过\n48: \n49: **Verification:** `reconciler.go` 编译通过；Reconcile 方法覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: Reconcile algorithm completeness 全部 10 个步骤\n50: \n51: ---\n52: \n53: ## T4. 实现 SetupWithManager 方法\n54: \n55: - [ ] 4.1 在 `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` 中实现 `SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error` 方法\n56: - [ ] 4.2 方法体：`return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).Complete(r)`\n57: - [ ] 4.3 运行 `go build ./pkg/agentd/...` 确认编译通过\n58: \n59: **Verification:** `SetupWithManager` 方法签名与 design.md §4.2 一致；编译零错误\n60: \n61: ---\n62: \n63: ## T5. 单元测试 — Reconcile 核心路径覆盖\n64: \n65: - [ ] 5.1 创建 `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go`\n66: - [ ] 5.2 定义测试辅助：\n67:   - `newTestScheme() *runtime.Scheme`：创建包含 `sandboxv1alpha1` 的 Scheme\n68:   - `newFakeReconciler(objects ...runtime.Object) *agentd.Reconciler`：使用 `fake.NewClientBuilder` 构建\n69:   - `newSandbox(ns, name string, annotations map[string]string) *sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox`：构造测试 Sandbox\n70: - [ ] 5.3 测试 `TestReconcile_SandboxNotFound`：fake client 中无 Sandbox → `Result{}`, `nil`\n71: - [ ] 5.4 测试 `TestReconcile_GetError`：使用自定义 client wrapper 注入 Get 错误 → `Result{}`, `err`\n72: - [ ] 5.5 测试 `TestReconcile_AnnotationMissing`：Sandbox 无 `last-activity-time` 注解 → `Result{}`, `nil`\n73: - [ ] 5.6 测试 `TestReconcile_AnnotationEmpty`：注解值为 `\"\"` → `Result{}`, `nil`\n74: - [ ] 5.7 测试 `TestReconcile_InvalidTimestamp`：注解值为 `\"not-a-timestamp\"` → `Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}`, `err != nil`\n75: - [ ] 5.8 测试 `TestReconcile_NotExpired`：注解值为 5 分钟前 → `Result{RequeueAfter: ~10m}`, `nil`，Sandbox 未被删除\n76: - [ ] 5.9 测试 `TestReconcile_Expired`：注解值为 20 分钟前 → Sandbox 被删除，`Result{}`, `nil`\n77: - [ ] 5.10 测试 `TestReconcile_DeleteNotFound`：Sandbox 在 Get 和 Delete 之间被删除 → `Result{}`, `nil`\n78: - [ ] 5.11 测试 `TestReconcile_DeleteError`：使用自定义 client wrapper 注入 Delete 错误 → `Result{}`, `err`\n79: - [ ] 5.12 测试 `TestReconcile_AtExpirationBoundary`：注解值恰好 15 分钟前 → `Result{RequeueAfter: >=0}`, `nil`（`After()` 返回 false）\n80: \n81: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/agentd/... -v -count=1` 全部通过；覆盖 design.md §6.1 测试矩阵全部 10 个场景\n82: \n83: ---\n84: \n85: ## T6. 单元测试 — SetupWithManager\n86: \n87: - [ ] 6.1 测试 `TestSetupWithManager`：使用 envtest 或 fake manager 验证 `SetupWithManager` 返回 `nil` 且无 panic\n88: \n89: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/agentd/... -run TestSetupWithManager -v` 通过\n90: \n91: ---\n92: \n93: ## T7. 实现 Binary Entry Point — cmd/agentd/main.go\n94: \n95: - [ ] 7.1 创建 `cmd/agentd/` 目录\n96: - [ ] 7.2 创建 `cmd/agentd/main.go`\n97: - [ ] 7.3 定义 `schemeBuilder = runtime.NewScheme()` 和 `setupLog = ctrl.Log.WithName(\"setup\")`\n98: - [ ] 7.4 `init()` 函数：`utilruntime.Must(scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))` + `utilruntime.Must(sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))`\n99: - [ ] 7.5 `main()` 函数：\n100:   - 解析 zap 日志选项：`opts := zap.Options{Development: true}`；`opts.BindFlags(flag.CommandLine)`；`flag.Parse()`\n101:   - `ctrl.SetLogger(zap.New(zap.UseFlagOptions(&opts)))`\n102:   - 构造 Manager：`ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{Scheme: schemeBuilder, Metrics: metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"}, HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\"})`\n103:   - Manager 构造失败 → `setupLog.Error` + `os.Exit(1)`\n104:   - 注册 Reconciler：`(&agentd.Reconciler{Client: mgr.GetClient(), Scheme: mgr.GetScheme()}).SetupWithManager(mgr)`\n105:   - 注册失败 → `setupLog.Error` + `os.Exit(1)`\n106:   - 启动 Manager：`mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler())`\n107:   - 启动失败 → `setupLog.Error` + `os.Exit(1)`\n108: - [ ] 7.6 导入依赖：`flag`, `os`, `runtime`, `utilruntime`, `sandboxv1alpha1`, `ctrl`, `zap`, `metricsserver`, `agentd`（内部包）\n109: - [ ] 7.7 运行 `go build ./cmd/agentd/...` 确认编译通过\n110: \n111: **Verification:** `cmd/agentd/main.go` 编译通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: Binary entry point 全部 3 个子需求（Scheme 注册、Manager 配置、Controller 注册与启动）\n112: \n113: ---\n114: \n115: ## T8. 依赖管理\n116: \n117: - [ ] 8.1 运行 `go mod tidy` 确保 `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` 和 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` 依赖正确\n118: - [ ] 8.2 确认 `go.mod` 和 `go.sum` 变更合理\n119: \n120: **Verification:** `go mod tidy` 无异常；`go build ./cmd/agentd/... ./pkg/agentd/...` 编译通过\n121: \n122: ---\n123: \n124: ## T9. 代码质量门禁\n125: \n126: - [ ] 9.1 运行 `go build ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` 确认编译通过\n127: - [ ] 9.2 运行 `go test ./pkg/agentd/... -v -count=1` 确认全部测试通过\n128: - [ ] 9.3 运行 `go test -race ./pkg/agentd/...` 确认无数据竞争\n129: - [ ] 9.4 运行 `go vet ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` 确认无警告\n130: - [ ] 9.5 运行 `go mod tidy` 确认无变更\n131: - [ ] 9.6 确认 `pkg/agentd/` 下每个 `*.go` 文件都有对应的 `*_test.go` 文件\n132: \n133: **Verification:** 以上 6 项全部通过；exit code 均为 0\n134: \n135: ---\n136: \n137: ## Task Dependencies\n138: \n139: ```\n140: T1 ──┐\n141:      ├──→ T3 ──→ T5 ──┐\n142: T2 ──┘     │          │\n143:            ↓          │\n144:            T4 ──→ T6 ─┤\n145:                       │\n146:            T7 ────────┤\n147:                       │\n148:            T8 ────────┤\n149:                       │\n150:                       ↓\n151:                      T9\n152: ```\n153: \n154: **Parallel execution:**\n155: - T1（workloadmanager 常量）和 T2（agentd 常量）可并行\n156: - T3（Reconcile 实现）需 T1 和 T2 完成后开始（依赖两个常量）\n157: - T4（SetupWithManager）需 T3 完成后开始\n158: - T5（Reconcile 测试）需 T3 完成后开始，可与 T6 并行\n159: - T7（binary entry point）需 T3 和 T4 完成后开始\n160: - T8（依赖管理）可与 T5/T6/T7 并行\n161: - T9 为最终门禁，需所有前置任务完成\n162: \n163: ---\n164: \n165: ## Acceptance Criteria\n166: \n167: | # | Criterion | Command |\n168: |---|-----------|---------|\n169: | AC1 | 编译通过 | `go build ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` |\n170: | AC2 | 全部测试通过 | `go test ./pkg/agentd/... -v -count=1` |\n171: | AC3 | 无竞态条件 | `go test -race ./pkg/agentd/...` |\n172: | AC4 | 无 lint 警告 | `go vet ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` |\n173: | AC5 | Reconcile 覆盖 10 个测试场景 | `go test ./pkg/agentd/... -run TestReconcile -v` |\n174: | AC6 | SetupWithManager 测试通过 | `go test ./pkg/agentd/... -run TestSetupWithManager -v` |\n175: | AC7 | Binary 编译成功 | `go build ./cmd/agentd/...` |\n176: | AC8 | SessionExpirationTimeout = 15min | 代码审查 `pkg/agentd/const.go` |\n177: | AC9 | LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\" | 代码审查 `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go` |\n178: | AC10 | 依赖清理 | `go mod tidy` 无变更 |\n179: | AC11 | 每个源文件有对应测试文件 | `ls pkg/agentd/*_test.go` |\n\n(End of file - total 179 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** pkg/agentd\n> **Language:** Go\n> **Size:** S\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-018/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-018/design.md`, `changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md`\n\n## T1. 定义常量 — pkg/workloadmanager/const.go\n\n- [ ] 1.1 创建 `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go`\n- [ ] 1.2 定义 `LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"`\n- [ ] 1.3 运行 `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 确认编译通过\n\n**Verification:** `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go` 存在；`LastActivityAnnotationKey` 值为 `\"last-activity-time\"`；编译零错误\n\n---\n\n## T2. 定义常量 — pkg/agentd/const.go\n","tru